SUMMARY:Game Escape Indie Showcase
DESCRIPTION:Come see a selection of locally made indie games brought to you by the creators behind them! \n\nA curation of locally made games presented by the developers behind them!\nFeaturing a performance by the BGSO Small Ensembles at 1-2 PM!\nParking is available in limited quantities on the street\, and the recommended parking lot is 1714 N Charles St.\n\nHosted by IGDA Baltimore.
URL:https://baltimoreindiegames.com/event/game-escape-indie-showcase/
LOCATION:Parkway Theatre\, 5 W North Ave\, Baltimore\, MD\, 21201\, United States
END:VEVENT
