SUMMARY:MSU Level Up Summit
DESCRIPTION:Morgan State University\n1700 E. Cold Spring Lane\, Baltimore\, MD 21251 \nJoin the Baltimore IGDA on September 27\, 2025 at Morgan State University for a full day of gaming\, innovation\, and community building! Participate in interactive panels from AAA Game Developers from the Baltimore IGDA\, witness the grand opening of the Esports Competition & Broadcast Lab\, and cheer on Morgan State and Howard University in the Battle of 295 Marvel Rivals competition for a custom championship belt. \nExperience the excitement live—MSU student broadcasters will stream all the behind-the-scenes tournament action from the Legacy Hall lobby. Spectators can watch in person from Legacy Hall and the Student Center theater for even more immersive viewing. Enjoy creative showcases from student talent and open gaming at the BEARcade in the Student Center. \nAll are welcome—students\, alumni\, families\, and the community. Admission is free with RSVP. All venues ADA accessible. \nOfficial RSVP here. https://events.morgan.edu/event/level-up-summit-empowering-futures-through-gaming \n 
URL:https://baltimoreindiegames.com/event/morgan-state-level-up-summit/
END:VEVENT
