SUMMARY:Game Fest at Columbia Central Library
DESCRIPTION:Age Group: Children\, Teens\, Adults\, Everyone \nEvent Details: Join Howard County Libraries for an exciting\, all-ages Game Fest at Central! Explore a variety of gaming experiences\, from board games and video games to D&D and tabletop RPGs. Enjoy live music from the Baltimore Gamer Symphony Orchestra & Choir\, participate in interactive workshops\, and connect with local community partners. \nWhether you’re a kid\, teen\, or adult\, there’s something for everyone! \nBIG members will be showing indie games.
URL:https://baltimoreindiegames.com/event/game-fest-at-columbia-central-library/
LOCATION:Central Branch Library\, 10375 Little Patuxent Parkway\, Columbia\, MD\, United States
END:VEVENT
