SUMMARY:Ludum Dare 58 [East Columbia Branch & Online]
DESCRIPTION:BIG is hosting an online site for the Ludum Dare 58 game jam all weekend on our Discord server (message Tony Li on Meetup for link) and in-person! \n\nFriday 7 PM – 9:30 PM: MOD Pizza Columbia Mall | Columbia\, MD\nSaturday 10 AM – 5 PM: Marvin Thomas Room\, East Columia Branch Library\nSunday 1 PM – 4:30 PM: Marvin Thomas Room\, East Columbia Branch Library\n\nWhether you’re a game jam veteran or have never made a video game before\, all are welcome to join us online and make a game in a weekend! Team up with other BIG members\, bring your own team\, or work solo. \nJoin us for the theme announcement\, then stay connected through the weekend to discuss game ideas\, find team members\, and coordinate on your jam entry. \nLudum Dare 58: https://ludumdare.com/ \nMeetup RSVP: https://www.meetup.com/baltimore-indie-game-developers-group/events/310831033/
URL:https://baltimoreindiegames.com/event/ludum-dare-58-central-branch-library-online/
LOCATION:East Columbia Branch
END:VEVENT
